{"allowModDistribution":true,"screenshots":[{"description":"Style still wip","id":614209,"title":"Elemental Armors","modId":561470,"url":"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/614/209/2022-09-11_17.png","thumbnailUrl":"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/thumbnails/614/209/310/172/2022-09-11_17.png"},{"description":"","id":459520,"title":"Siren Aquarium","modId":561470,"url":"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/459/520/2022-05-05_10.png","thumbnailUrl":"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/thumbnails/459/520/310/172/2022-05-05_10.png"},{"description":"Firenandos: Magma,Soul and familiar variants","id":458087,"title":"Fire Golems","modId":561470,"url":"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/458/87/2022-04-29_15.png","thumbnailUrl":"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/thumbnails/458/87/310/172/2022-04-29_15.png"},{"description":"Quartz formations and breezes can spawn in these forests, as well as a new flower that crafts into glowstone dust.","id":1066592,"title":"A Flashing Archwood Forest","modId":561470,"url":"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/1066/592/2025-01-14_11.png","thumbnailUrl":"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/thumbnails/1066/592/310/172/2025-01-14_11.png"},{"description":"Lava lakes and blackstone formations and cinderflowers spawn in this fiery forest.","id":1066593,"title":"A Blazing Archwood Forest","modId":561470,"url":"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/1066/593/2025-01-14_11.png","thumbnailUrl":"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/thumbnails/1066/593/310/172/2025-01-14_11.png"},{"description":"Meeting point of Flashing, Flourishing and Cascading forests","id":1066618,"title":"A meeting of three Archwood biomes","modId":561470,"url":"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/1066/618/2025-01-14_11.png","thumbnailUrl":"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/thumbnails/1066/618/310/172/2025-01-14_11.png"},{"description":"In the waters near the Cascading Forest, lilypads and corals also spawn.","id":1066619,"title":"A Cascadin